subdomain)
- Internationalized domain name (IDN) are now decoded to unicode for better display
- Dynamic language switching without the need to restart MoM
- Change shortcuts on Mac OS X for deleting an item, go to parent level or root level to be
consistant with the shortcuts used in the Finder
- Fix the offset of the text in the proxy tab located in the preferences dialog
- Fix the error messages from SOAPI that were always in french even if MoM was set in another
language

